        "richtext": "<p>A premium blend of Merino Wool, Tencel, and Spandex delivers <em>softness, stretch, </em>and <em>performance</em> in every layer.</p><ul><li><strong>Merino Wool</strong> - Regulates temperature, wicks moisture, resists odor.</li><li><strong>Tencel</strong> - Smooth, breathable, and eco-friendly.</li><li><strong>Spandex</strong> - Built-in stretch for total freedom of movement.</li></ul><p><strong>270 gsm</strong> midweight fabric = warm, breathable, and <em>ready for anything.</em></p>",
